        Un grand merci à tous mes sponsors et partenaires pour leur aide précieuse et leur soutien!
    </p>
    <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl !mt-8">Entreprises</h2>
    <div class="grid items-center gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="flex justify-center md:col-span-3">
            <a href="https://www.iomedia.ch" target="_blank" class="w-full md:w-3/5">
                <img src="{{ asset('images/sponsors/iomedia.svg') }}" alt="" class="w-full">
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center md:col-span-3">
            <a href="https://www.iomedia.ch" target="_blank" class="w-full md:w-2/5">
                <img src="{{ asset('images/sponsors/nendaz-tourisme.svg') }}" alt="" class="w-full">
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
            <a href="https://bornettransports.ch/" target="_blank" class="w-2/5 md:w-2/3">
                <img src="{{ asset('images/sponsors/bornet-transports.jpg') }}" alt="" class="w-full">
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
            <a href="https://latico.ch/" target="_blank" class="w-3/5 md:w-full">
                <img src="{{ asset('images/sponsors/latico.png') }}" alt="" class="w-full">
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
            <a href="https://lelabdesmontagnes.ch/" target="_blank" class="w-1/3 md:w-3/5">
                <img src="{{ asset('images/sponsors/lelab.png') }}" alt="" class="w-full">
